abstract: >
  MATSim LLM Plugins provides integration between MATSim (Multi-Agent Transport Simulation)
  and large language models (LLMs) using an OpenAI-compatible tool-calling interface.
  It enables agents to perform structured, context-aware decision-making during simulation,
  supporting both replanning and within-day adaptive behavior.

